[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1108","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0878","title":"WU-FTPD 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 及其相关 FTP 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送特制的 MAPPING_CHDIR 命令触发该漏洞，导致越界内存写入并最终获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响大量使用 WU-FTPD 的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0878"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.740","remediation":"建议立即升级 WU-FTPD 至 2.6.0 及以上版本（该漏洞已在后续版本中修复），或迁移至 vsftpd、ProFTPD 等仍在积极维护的 FTP 服务端。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中禁用 FTP 服务，改用 SFTP/SCP 替代文件传输协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/599"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1689","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1064","title":"WindowMaker 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"WindowMaker 0.52 至 0.60.0 版本存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞。当以超长程序名（argv[0]）执行 WindowMaker 时，攻击者可触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标系统拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响版本范围较广，攻击条件简单，无需复杂认证即可利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1064"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.880","remediation":"建议升级 WindowMaker 至 0.61.0 或更高版本，当前最新稳定版 0.96.0 已彻底修复该 argv[0] 缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可采用以下缓解措施：(1) 使用 grsecurity/PaX 内核补丁开启地址空间布局随机化（ASLR）和不可执行内存页（NX）；(2) 在启动包装脚本中校验传入 argv[0] 长度，截断超长程序名后调用 WindowMaker；(3) 禁止在 SetUID 或网络暴露环境中运行 WindowMaker。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93555317429630&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582070508957&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/596","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1064","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1064.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8xf-jm9x-c783/GHSA-q8xf-jm9x-c783.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/596/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0184","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0184.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0668","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 ActiveX 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 的 scriptlet.typelib ActiveX 控件被错误标记为\"对脚本安全\"，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页诱导用户访问，利用该控件在用户系统上写入任意文件并执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5 及早期版本，Bubbleboy 蠕虫即利用此漏洞传播，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0668"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-08-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.493","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 提供的补丁，该补丁移除了 scriptlet.typelib ActiveX 控件的\"安全可脚本\"标记。如无法安装补丁，可在 Internet Explorer 中将 Internet 安全区域设置为\"高\"并禁用 ActiveX 控件，或通过注册表设置该控件的 kill bit（CLSID: {06290BD3-48AA-11D2-8432-006008C3FBFC}）阻止其在 IE 中加载。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ240308","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/598","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19468","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0668.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0668","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0668.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0668.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mf4v-53v8-r6cm/GHSA-mf4v-53v8-r6cm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0668.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1311b123-7ec1-4ac2-beca-9860a9f96c2e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0184.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0184.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0184.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0364","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0364.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0743","title":"Trn 本地用户符号链接覆盖其他用户文件漏洞","description":"Trn 新闻阅读器存在本地符号链接漏洞，本地用户可通过创建符号链接指向其他用户文件，在特定条件下覆盖目标文件内容。该漏洞源于程序在处理临时文件时未对符号链接进行充分校验，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低但影响范围有限（仅影响同系统用户），CVSS 评分 2.1 危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0743"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.870","remediation":"升级 Trn 至修复了不安全临时文件创建的版本（trn 4.0-test77 之后版本），或在 Linux 内核中通过 fs.protected_symlinks=1 启用符号链接保护（sysctl -w fs.protected_symlinks=1）。如无法升级，建议将 /tmp 挂载为 noexec,nosuid 并使用 private /tmp 模式（systemd 默认启用），同时在 cron 中定期清理 /tmp 下的 Trn 临时文件。使用 tmpfiles.d 或 pam_namespace 对每位用户隔离临时目录可彻底阻断此类攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3144","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0743.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0743","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0743.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0743.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w5gh-xpm5-prq2/GHSA-w5gh-xpm5-prq2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0743.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88064/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f7f02ce6-65e9-4ce7-aacb-b8528cfb6e7e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0364.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0345","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0345.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0732","title":"Debian smtp-refuser 日志记录本地任意文件删除漏洞","description":"Debian smtp-refuser 软件包的日志记录功能存在不安全符号链接处理漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建符号链接将日志文件重定向指向系统任意文件，利用日志写入操作删除目标文件，造成拒绝服务或本地权限提升。该漏洞需本地用户权限方可利用，攻击条件受限，影响 Debian 系统中的 smtp-refuser 软件包。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0732"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.500","remediation":"Debian 已移除 smtp-refuser 软件包，建议迁移至 Postfix 或 Exim 等现代 MTA。若仍需使用，需将日志目录所有权设为专用系统用户，且日志文件创建时使用 O_EXCL 标志防止跟随符号链接，同时以低权限用户运行守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0732","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0732.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0732","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0732.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0732.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rh82-9f2f-4h42/GHSA-rh82-9f2f-4h42.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0732.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88036/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990823b.data","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fc08d088-1503-41d7-bd11-adf99800d367.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0345.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0348","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0348.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0734","title":"Cisco CiscoSecure ACS 默认配置权限绕过漏洞","description":"CiscoSecure ACS（访问控制服务器）存在默认配置安全漏洞，远程攻击者无需任何认证即可直接修改服务器数据库，导致权限提升、配置篡改或服务中断。该漏洞源于出厂默认设置未对管理接口实施访问控制，攻击者只需网络可达即可利用。影响 CiscoSecure ACS 早期版本，建议立即修改默认配置并启用认证机制。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0734"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.753","remediation":"立即升级 CiscoSecure ACS 至修复该漏洞的最新版本；在 ACS 管理界面中启用数据库访问认证功能，要求所有数据库修改操作须提供有效管理员凭据；同时在防火墙上限制仅允许受信管理 IP 访问 ACS 的数据库管理端口（默认 TCP 2000），作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3133","https://tools.cisco.com/security/center/content/CiscoSecurityAdvisory/cisco-sa-19990819-dbaccess","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0734.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0734","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0734.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0734.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7x9m-2pr4-mhrf/GHSA-7x9m-2pr4-mhrf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0734.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87034/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000736.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0348.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0358","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0358.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0740","title":"Red Hat Linux in.telnetd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 系统自带的 in.telnetd Telnet 守护进程存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 TERM 环境变量，触发服务进程异常终止，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.2、5.2、6.0 等多个版本，攻击条件低，仅需网络可达即可实施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0740"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议立即禁用 in.telnetd 服务并改用 SSH 远程登录：注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中 telnet 行后重启 inetd 服务。如必须使用 telnet，请升级至 Red Hat Linux 6.2 及以上版本。对于已达生命周期的 Red Hat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0，建议迁移至受支持的企业级发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/594","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0740.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0740","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0740.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0740.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-chv2-pxjh-365q/GHSA-chv2-pxjh-365q.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0740.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0358.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0506","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0506.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0725","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 双字节代码页信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 及 4.0 版本在处理双字节代码页（中文、韩文、日文）时存在配置缺陷，当服务器默认语言设置为上述语言时，远程攻击者可通过特制 HTTP 请求绕过文件解析机制，直接查看 ASP 等脚本文件的源代码，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0/4.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.1，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0725"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-022 提供的对应语言版本补丁。IIS 3.0 用户安装 IIS 3.0 补丁，IIS 4.0 用户安装重新发布的 IIS 4.0 补丁（修复了回归错误）。补丁须与 IIS 语言版本匹配而非服务器默认语言。如无法安装补丁，建议升级至 IIS 5.0 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ233335","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/477","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-022","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2302"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0506.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0555","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0555.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0741","title":"QMS CrownNet Unix实用程序认证绕过漏洞","description":"QMS CrownNet 是 QMS 2060 打印服务器上运行的 Unix 管理工具，存在严重身份认证缺陷：该工具允许任意用户以 root 权限直接登录系统而无需密码验证。攻击者只需通过网络连接到目标打印服务器上的对应管理端口即可触发，无需提前获取任何凭证。成功利用后，攻击者可获得打印服务器的完全控制权，进而读取、修改或删除打印机配置及网络设置。此漏洞影响运行 CrownNet Unix 实用程序的 QMS 2060 系列设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0741"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-19","updated":"1999-08-19","remediation":"立即将 CrownNet 固件升级至 3.0 或更高版本（该版本已修复默认 root 无密码登录问题）；若无法升级固件，则通过防火墙规则限制 TCP 端口 515（lpd）和 CrownNet 管理端口（默认 2000/TCP）仅允许可信 IP 访问；如无需远程管理功能，建议在 CrownNet 配置界面中直接禁用 Unix 实用程序服务；将 QMS 2060 打印机部署于独立隔离 VLAN，避免暴露在通用网络中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0741.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0741","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/a1bd988e57a056ba1f06c9d4970f9f19b2540605/1999/CVE-1999-0741/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0741.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0741.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hmmr-pvfg-gcfv/GHSA-hmmr-pvfg-gcfv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0741.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0555.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0381","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0381.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0747","title":"BSDi Symmetric Multiprocessing 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BSDi Symmetric Multiprocessing (SMP) 系统存在拒绝服务漏洞。当系统处于高 CPU 负载状态时，本地攻击者可通过调用 fstat 系统函数触发该漏洞，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 BSDi SMP 版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需要具有本地访问权限且系统处于高负载状态才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0747"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.370","remediation":"升级到 BSDi 的 SMP 补丁版本（如 BSD/OS 4.0.1 或更高），该版本已修复高 CPU 负载下 fstat 调用导致的拒绝服务问题。由于 BSDi 操作系统已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统（如 FreeBSD 或 Linux）以获取持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/589","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.BSI.4.10.9908170253560.19291-100000%40saturn.psn.net"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0381.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0745","title":"IBM AIX pdnsd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1/4.2 系统中 C Set++ 编译器附带的 Source Code Browser Program Database Name Server Daemon (pdnsd) 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向 pdnsd 服务发送特制请求触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致服务崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 AIX 4.1 及 4.2 版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0745"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.130","remediation":"立即升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续维护包中修复。如无法升级，可禁用 pdnsd 服务（/usr/bin/pdnsd），在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 pdnsd 行并重启 inetd 以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-059.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/590","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0745.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0745","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/a1bd988e57a056ba1f06c9d4970f9f19b2540605/1999/CVE-1999-0745/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0745.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0745.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1261.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0745.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0600.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0600.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0606","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0606.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0753","title":"Hughes Technologies Mini SQL w3-msql CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Hughes Technologies 开发的 Mini SQL (mSQL) 2.0 及 2.0.10 版本中，w3-msql CGI 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制 HTTP 请求利用该脚本读取服务器上受限制目录中的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 mSQL 2.0 系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0753"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.113","remediation":"立即升级到 mSQL 3.x 或更高版本，该版本已移除存在漏洞的 w3-msql CGI 脚本。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中删除或禁用 w3-msql 脚本，并通过 .htaccess 或 Nginx/Apache 访问控制规则限制对 /cgi-bin/ 目录的访问，仅允许授权 IP 调用。作为长期方案，建议迁移至 MySQL/MariaDB 等仍在维护的数据库产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/591","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19466","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1231f6f5f21cc87f3264c90adadd01cbb12e76ba/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0753.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0753","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0753.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0753.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3pqj-chvj-wmcp/GHSA-3pqj-chvj-wmcp.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/msql_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0753.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0606.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0606.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0606.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0379","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0379.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0746","title":"SuSE Linux in.identd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 6.2 及之前版本以及 Slackware Linux 3.2/3.6 中 in.identd 服务存在默认配置缺陷，该服务在处理请求时设置了 120 秒的请求间隔等待时间，远程攻击者可利用此机制向目标系统发送大量连接请求，耗尽系统资源，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版本，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0746"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.247","remediation":"升级 SuSE Linux 至 6.3 或更高版本，或禁用 in.identd 服务（`/etc/init.d/identd stop && chkconfig identd off`）。如必须使用 identd，修改配置文件降低请求间隔时间或添加连接速率限制，防止远程攻击者利用 120 秒等待间隔耗尽连接资源造成拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/587","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19463"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0379.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0386","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0386.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0749","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 Telnet 客户端缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98 系统的 Telnet 客户端存在堆缓冲区溢出漏洞，当用户连接至恶意 Telnet 服务器时，攻击者可通过发送特制的 Telnet 参数触发该漏洞，导致堆内存损坏，进而可能造成拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 和 Windows 98 系统，需用户主动发起 Telnet 连接方可触发，属于客户端侧漏洞，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0749"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.607","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-033 提供的 Telnet 客户端补丁，Windows 95 用户通过 https://www.microsoft.com 下载，Windows 98/98 SE 用户通过 Windows Update 或 https://www.microsoft.com/windows98/downloads/contents/WUCritical/Telnet/Default.asp 获取。由于 Windows 95/98 已停止支持，建议升级到 Windows 10 或更高版本以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/586","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-033","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19462"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0386.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0386.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0386.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0679","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0679.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0888","title":"Oracle Intelligent Agent 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Oracle Intelligent Agent 组件中的 dbsnmp 工具存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置 ORACLE_HOME 环境变量为恶意路径，使 dbsnmp 加载并执行攻击者控制的 nmiconf.tcl 脚本，从而获取 dbsnmp 进程权限。该漏洞影响 Oracle 8/8.1.5 版本，攻击者需拥有本地操作系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0888"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:15.940","remediation":"升级 Oracle Intelligence Agent 至 8.1.6 以上版本。限制 dbsnmp 可执行文件的执行权限，仅允许授权用户运行。设置 ORACLE_HOME 目录权限为 750，确保 nmiconf.tcl 脚本不被非授权用户修改。在操作系统层面使用最小权限原则运行 Oracle Agent 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/585","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19461"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0679.toml"}]